{"tid":1650450,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"見到連登有人話和勇已經升級到無得再升 我個人有個睇法：","createTime":"2019-10-13T03:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:45:07.000Z","uid":216800,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abd9d35c344114d64653495fcaee69d4ae70f712","tid":1650450,"uid":216800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:18:54.000Z","msg":"基於預告式集會黎講<br />\n狗方好容易研究到包圍路線<br />\n亦都基於要令指揮官增加管理難度<br />\n所諗到嘅戰術<br />\n就係以後行動「小隊化」<br />\n小隊盡量控制20人以內並以代號稱呼及小隊成立理念<br />\n（例如：「仇士小隊」，我地係個別嘅十一人，我地要求立即解散警隊，喺哩度，即使我倒下，擁有個別自我嘅人都會接管我地嘅意志，死亡對我地黎講無任何意義！）<br />\n<br />\n當小隊做嘅野越黎越多，大家越黎越多人認識到小隊理念，所做嘅野就越黎越合理化，所謂傳說 說係咁嘅一回事。<br />\n<br />\n擴大效果，<br />\n可以喺現場留低小隊嘅隊徽。"},{"pid":"f302c9f9debe11d3da1c0a7851a0401dab961241","tid":1650450,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:19:26.000Z","msg":"炸彈?"},{"pid":"be39920d0af40d85d4fef43835d0441a3db43f1b","tid":1650450,"uid":311198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:20:07.000Z","msg":"但係一定要做足文宣 事前事後 或者唔係又比人話係鬼"},{"pid":"046ee06daa27030b6bf7876da22a8f4a277b58a0","tid":1650450,"uid":28252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"唔一定係升級先叫有成效，就算打機都唔係一直點武力點武力點武力"},{"pid":"352e7415fd2d264eafc9102e3b7698bd5d4177a6","tid":1650450,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:25:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"266d3bf231dcf82c935a22cab9617da7c2060acb","tid":1650450,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T03:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"920bc47851ee758b7638bbe7183ae260d8429f26","tid":1650450,"uid":2168